5","text":"The voice of the LORD breaketh the cedars; yea, the LORD breaketh the cedars of Lebanon."},{"id":"recWC5zST36f1n8QI","ref":"Ps.29.6","text":"He maketh them also to skip like a calf; Lebanon and Sirion like a young unicorn."},{"id":"recYzCgVohv6Ngpak","ref":"Ps.29.7","text":"The voice of the LORD divideth the flames of fire."},{"id":"rectDlZZ3urqOKaXg","ref":"Ps.29.8","text":"The voice of the LORD shaketh the wilderness; the LORD shaketh the wilderness of Kadesh."}]}
